msgid "So navañca kammaṃ na karoti, purāṇañca kammaṃ phussa phussa byantīkaroti. "
msgstr "They don’t perform any new deeds, and old deeds are eliminated by experiencing their results little by little. "

msgctxt "an4.195:7.4"
msgid "Sandiṭṭhikā nijjarā akālikā ehipassikā opaneyyikā paccattaṃ veditabbā viññūhi. "
msgstr "This wearing away is visible in this very life, immediately effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know it for themselves. "

msgctxt "an4.195:7.5"
msgid "Passasi no tvaṃ, vappa, taṃ ṭhānaṃ yatonidānaṃ purisaṃ dukkhavedaniyā āsavā assaveyyuṃ abhisamparāyan”ti? "
msgstr "Do you see any reason why defilements giving rise to painful feelings would defile that person in the next life?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.195:7.6"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an4.195:8.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, vappa, "
msgstr "“What do you think, Vappa? "

msgctxt "an4.195:8.2"
msgid "ye manosamārambhapaccayā uppajjanti āsavā vighātapariḷāhā, manosamārambhā paṭiviratassa evaṃsa te āsavā vighātapariḷāhā na honti. "
msgstr "There are distressing and feverish defilements that arise because of undertaking mental activity. These don’t occur in someone who avoids such mental activity. "

msgctxt "an4.195:8.3"
msgid "So navañca kammaṃ na karoti, purāṇañca kammaṃ phussa phussa byantīkaroti. "
msgstr "They don’t perform any new deeds, and old deeds are eliminated by experiencing their results little by little. "

msgctxt "an4.195:8.4"
msgid "Sandiṭṭhikā nijjarā akālikā ehipassikā opaneyyikā paccattaṃ veditabbā viññūhi. "
